If you’re an introvert, empath, homebody, or just plain shy, read this twice:⁣
⁣
💥 You *don’t* have to be an outgoing, type-A go-getter to start and grow a successful business. 💥⁣
⁣
Today on #MarieTV, media strategist and B-School grad @angelacheetv joins me to help YOU build unshakable confidence in your unique voice and grow a best-selling brand — even if you’re introverted.⁣
⁣
The dangerous myth of “what it takes” to be an entrepreneur squashes thousands of aspiring entrepreneurs before they even get started. Don’t let it stop you, too.⁣
⁣
If you dream about starting a business but struggle with self-doubt, this is a must-watch. Go to MarieForleo.com/blog or 🎧 listen to #TheMarieForleoPodcast on @Spotify or @ApplePodcasts for the full episode.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣
P.S. If you’re a business owner or want to be, get your butt into our first ever B-School summer session — link in bio or JoinBSchool.com/enroll 💗⁣⁣⁣
⁣
⁣

⁣Imagine that all of your wildest dreams have come true…⁣
⁣
What happens next? 🤔⁣⁣
⁣⁣
For Erin Benzakein (@floretflower) — B-School grad and founder of Floret Flower Farm 🌸 — this is the question she’s asking herself. But it didn’t start that way.⁣⁣
⁣⁣
In her words, “It started in my backyard and it stayed in my backyard for years. Really just me fumbling along, making a thousand mistakes, not making any money, killing so many plants, just really sucking at it for a long time.”⁣⁣
⁣⁣
15 years, 40,000 bouquets 💐, 3 books, and one show on @magnolianetwork later, Erin is one of the nation’s leading farmer-florists. My favorite thing about her? Her honesty and wisdom about what it *really* takes to stay true to your heart and make it as an entrepreneur. 💗⁣⁣
⁣⁣
If you’ve ever wondered if you have what it takes to turn your unlikely dream into reality, today's episode is a must-watch. Go to MarieForleo.com/blog or 🎧 listen to #TheMarieForleoPodcast on @Spotify or @ApplePodcasts for the full episode.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣
P.S. Ready to turn your dream business into a reality? Our first-ever B-School Summer Session is open now! JoinBSchool.com/enroll 😘⁣⁣
